column5: Hello Everyone, just want to share my morning. Went out to a local river, through on brown stone fly and bang This was the outcome. This is my first from this river, i feel as my first Salmon landed this year i feel i caught this late....LOL Here is some raw footage of the takedown, It put a smile on my face as i said Good Morning.....enjoy !  Fish On Pt-1 Fish On Pt-2
What a fish!!!,looks almost to big for that water.lol.
Very nice! Cant wait for my first of the year!
